{"_path":"/guide/what-is-a-bess-battery-energy-storage-system","_dir":"guide","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"What Is a BESS? Battery Energy Storage Systems Explained","description":"What is a BESS? Learn how battery energy storage systems work, their components, use cases, and how to choose a provider for your project.","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"what-is-a-bess-battery-energy-storage-systems-explained"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"What Is a BESS? Battery Energy Storage Systems Explained"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A BESS, or battery energy storage system, stores electricity so it can be used later. By charging when energy is cheap or abundant and discharging when it is expensive or scarce, a BESS helps businesses, utilities, and grids cut costs, improve resilience, and integrate renewable energy."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"how-a-bess-works"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"How a BESS Works"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A battery energy storage system absorbs electrical energy, stores it chemically in batteries, and releases it on demand. Core functions include:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Charging"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Drawing power from the grid or on-site generation such as solar."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Storing"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Holding energy in battery cells until it is needed."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Discharging"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Delivering power back to loads or the grid."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Managing"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Software and controls decide when and how to charge and discharge."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"key-components-of-a-bess"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Key Components of a BESS"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Battery cells and modules"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Store the energy; chemistries include lithium-ion, iron flow, and others."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Power conversion system (inverter)"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Converts between the battery's DC and the grid's AC."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Energy management software"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Optimizes dispatch, monitors health, and integrates with the grid."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Enclosure and thermal management"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Houses and cools the system safely."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"common-use-cases-for-a-bess"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Common Use Cases for a BESS"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Peak shaving & demand charges"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Discharge during peaks to lower commercial energy bills."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Backup power"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Keep critical loads running through outages, including data centers."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Renewable firming"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Smooth solar and wind output and shift it to when it is needed."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Grid services"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Provide frequency regulation, capacity, and other utility-scale services."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Microgrids"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Enable resilient, islandable local power systems."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"bess-battery-technologies"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BESS Battery Technologies"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"While lithium-ion dominates, other chemistries suit specific needs:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lithium-ion"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - High energy density and broad availability for most applications."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Iron flow"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Consistent output over long durations, used by "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/dir/ess_inc"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ESS, Inc."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Gravity & hydrogen storage"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Long-duration approaches offered by "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/dir/energy_vault"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Energy Vault"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"how-to-choose-a-bess-provider"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"How to Choose a BESS Provider"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Match the provider to your project scale, technology needs, and delivery model. Options range from full-stack manufacturers like "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/dir/fluence"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Fluence"}]},{"type":"text","value":" and turnkey utility-scale providers like "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/dir/wartsila"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Wärtsilä"}]},{"type":"text","value":", to software-first platforms like "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/dir/stem"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Stem"}]},{"type":"text","value":" and rental, plug-and-play units from "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/dir/aggreko"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Aggreko"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"frequently-asked-questions"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Frequently Asked Questions"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"what-does-bess-stand-for"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"What does BESS stand for?"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BESS stands for battery energy storage system, a system that stores electrical energy in batteries for later use."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"how-long-can-a-bess-store-energy"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"How long can a BESS store energy?"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Most lithium-ion systems are designed for a few hours of discharge, while long-duration technologies such as iron flow, gravity, and hydrogen storage can hold and deliver energy for many hours or longer."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"what-is-the-difference-between-a-bess-and-a-generator"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"What is the difference between a BESS and a generator?"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A BESS stores and discharges electricity instantly and cleanly for a limited duration, while a generator produces power from fuel and can run as long as fuel is supplied. Many sites combine both for instant and extended backup."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"how-big-can-a-bess-be"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"How big can a BESS be?"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Systems range from kilowatt-hour units for small commercial sites to megawatt and gigawatt-hour installations for utility-scale grid projects."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ready to compare providers? See our "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/best/bess-companies"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"best BESS companies"}]},{"type":"text","value":" guide or "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"browse all listings"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"how-a-bess-works","depth":2,"text":"How a BESS Works"},{"id":"key-components-of-a-bess","depth":2,"text":"Key Components of a BESS"},{"id":"common-use-cases-for-a-bess","depth":2,"text":"Common Use Cases for a BESS"},{"id":"bess-battery-technologies","depth":2,"text":"BESS Battery Technologies"},{"id":"how-to-choose-a-bess-provider","depth":2,"text":"How to Choose a BESS Provider"},{"id":"frequently-asked-questions","depth":2,"text":"Frequently Asked Ques